<p>
<lb n="1"/>lakṣmīśanābhihēmābjā dvāṇīvibhu ra 
<lb n="2"/>jāyata <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tasya pādasarōjātā tpaṁḍabhū 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>mīśvarō jani <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> tasyāsvayē bhava dasau bhuvi kaṁṭa 
<lb n="4"/>bhūpa stīvrāsikṛttabalavatkaḍiyābha 
<lb n="5"/>vīraḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> nellūrisiddhinṛpabhīṣaṇakuṁ 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>bhikuṁbha prōnmuktamauktikavirā 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>jitavīrabhūmiḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> tasmā dabhū 
<lb n="8"/>tkēśavadhāruṇīśa stārādritārā 
<lb n="9"/>gaṇacārukīrttiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> prītyā vahā 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṁ nadanṛpālaputrīṁ bimmāṁbi 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>kāṁ haṁnasamānayānāṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
<lb n="12"/>tābhyā mabhū dgōṁkadharādhinā 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>dha ssauṁdaryyaśauryyōjvalara 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>tnahāraḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> kṛṣṇābthijābhyā miva śaṁ 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>barāri rudrādrijābhyā miva tā 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>rakāriḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> padmēva viṣṇō rggiri jēva 
<lb n="17"/>śaṁbbhō ssī tēva rāmasya śacīva ji 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ṣṇōḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> vippaṟtipōtakṣitipālapu 
<lb n="19" break="no"/>trī mēḍāṁbi kāsī dbhuvi tasya patnī <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
<lb n="20"/>tābhyāṁ sūnu rajāya tāyata 
<lb n="21"/>bhujaśrīkēśavōrvvīśvarō dhīmā nī 
<lb n="22" break="no"/>vanikaṁḍravāṭiviṣayakṣīrābthila 
<lb n="23" break="no"/>kṣmīdhavaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> bāhāsipravidāritārima 
<lb n="24" break="no"/>davatkuṁbhīṁdrakuṁbhasthalōnmuktavyakta 
<lb n="25"/>saraktamauktikamaṇibhrājiṣṇughōrāvahaḥ (incomplete) <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
</p>

